*Notes and Workarounds:*
This is probably due to the fact that JIRA cannot apply the default application access to _jira-users_ group. Please verify if _jira-users_ group was given the _JIRA Administrators_ permission in the Global Permissions. If so, please remove it and you should be all set. :)

