h3. ***Cause of OOME***
So far this affects instance with changeitem > 1500000 items
{code:sql}
jira=# select count(*) from changeitem;
  count
---------
 1500000
(1 row)
{code}

h5.steps to reproduce
# set the JIRA language to anything other than US English for one of the users (or on the system level);
# proceed with an operation that would trigger a notification that would include the _Description field_;
# see the _Description_ in the received email - the field content is there, but the title is not.
